      "span_text": "More advanced fitting of the TEM images using the software Pebbles uses the grayscale intensity to extrapolate the true extension of a spherical particle. Thus, the TEM diameters evaluated using Pebbles are consistently larger than the manually measured diameters and in excellent agreement with the diameters determined by SAXS."
